data.description: Welcome to this quiet community near Capital Beach in West Lincoln! This townhome has 3 total bedrooms, with the primary bedroom on first floor equipped with a fireplace and a full bath. Additionally, there is Main Floor laundry, large open living room plus informal dining room. The open stairway off living room Leads to two bedrooms and another full bath upstairs, a fenced backyard with nice patio area! Last but not least, this is one of the few options with a two stall garage.
